videos.description: Arike Ogunbowale runs the fast break and flicks a nice pass to Allisha Gray for the finish.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Ogunbowale drops a dime to Gray on the break) 2022/07/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ogunbowale drops a dime to Gray on the break

videos.description: Kayla Thornton takes a hard bump but is somehow able to flip a pass to Teaira McCowan for the tough and-1 finish.

tracking.trackingName: WNBA_One-Play (Thornton finds McCowan for the and-1 finish) 2022/07/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thornton finds McCowan for the and-1 finish

videos.description: Julie Allemand darts a nice pass through traffic to Emma Meeseman inside for the and-1 score.
